{
  "stem": "23090.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He bled to death.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was the end of the kitchen routine with us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were there for maybe another two or three weeks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were sent out to another camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Kaufbeuren, I was probably about six weeks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Six weeks in Kaufbeuren.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, from there, we went to Augsburg.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Augsburg, I was-- this was a work-- another work camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went on these trucks that-- that were-- I remember that that were gassed or fueled by-- they had these tanks on the side of the cab.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they would put like shavings, wood shavings, and so on, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so I remember that, because we had to stop every once in a while and get these shavings and sort of knock them back in, and continue on in these trucks.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we got to this camp in these trucks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We got into this Bavarian forest.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was these huge trees.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when we got into this place, it was like totally, completely covered with trees.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when we finally got to the facility, it was a Messerschmitt facility, it was an airplane facility, where they were building airplanes.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was completely camouflaged, and I was doing-- I was wiring something, in a cockpit, and the people that worked with me, or I work with, were French.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't know if they were French prisoners, or whatever, or if they were cooperating with the Germans, or were some sort of engineers.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But they were very nice to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they would bring me some-- an egg once in a while, and so on, so forth.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Of all the camps, that was probably one of the nicest camps that I was in, which was a work camp.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
